WN, Glasgow, 2018.07.06
-----------------------
(waqarnabi@gmail.com)



See README files in child folders for more details.

./fortran
----------
* Fortran code for 2D shallow water from Kampf's text.
* Self-contained, no additional input files needed.


./opencl-hetero
---------------
* OpenCL code for the 2D shallow water model
* Heterogenuous/portable code, tested on host-only (no opencl at all), cpu-as-device, gpu, and fpga.
* Perl based build script can be used to target appropriate device.
* Multiple functionally equivalent kernel versions (primarily to test effect of channels/pipes and smart-caching).



